CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is manually populated. This field is used to automatically select which risk grade template should be used as the template for a risk rating review during creation. To use this field, you can set the field name from the object you selected in LLC_BI__Template_Object_Type__c. You must use "Template_Object_Field_Value__c" field as well for this field to work appropriately.
CustomField.label: Template Object Field Name
